window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The tides of war surround Damien, birthing life into his army and bringing additional power to his stats. With a timeline to beat, a hunger for justice, and a passion for his family, he'll dominate anyone foolish enough to oppose him. New enemy or old, all will break against the strength of his will.</p> <p>Join Tribe Moonguard for this daring 5th installment.</p>"; 
